message: The Ministry of Health and partners will recognise and motivate outstanding health workers, entities, services and products in the upcoming Heroes in Health Awards. The objective of these awards is that by shining light on the outstanding contributions of; individual, community, nonprofit, public and private players in the health sector, they will be rallied to innovate, serve the public better and to embrace global trends in the delivery of efficient healthcare to Ugandaâ€™s citizens. The public choice awards officiated by H E Yoweri Kaguta Museveni will take place on Friday 6 November, 2020 at Kampala Serena Hotel.
